import Bilingual from '../../components/Bilingual.astro';
import CodeTabs from '../../components/CodeTabs.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Python VM & Bytecode · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Languages / Python VM</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">虚拟机与字节码</span><span slot="en">VM & Bytecode</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">Python 常被笼统称为"解释型语言"，但 CPython 的执行并非逐行解释源码——它有一条完整的<b>编译流水线</b>：源码先被解析为 <b>AST</b>，再编译为<b>字节码</b>（<code>.pyc</code>），最后由<b>栈式虚拟机</b>逐条执行。理解这条流水线，是看懂 Python 性能瓶颈、<code>dis</code> 反汇编、以及 GIL/协程底层机制的前提。点击下方各阶段查看详情。</span>
          <span slot="en">Python is loosely called "interpreted", but CPython doesn't interpret source line-by-line — it runs a full <b>compilation pipeline</b>: source is parsed into an <b>AST</b>, compiled to <b>bytecode</b> (<code>.pyc</code>), then executed by a <b>stack-based virtual machine</b>. Understanding this pipeline is prerequisite to grasping Python's performance limits, <code>dis</code> disassembly, and the internals of GIL/coroutines. Click each stage below.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- 交互：Python 执行流水线 -->
    <div class="glass p-5" data-viz="py-pipeline">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <button class="btn pl-btn btn-primary" data-stage="src"><span data-lang="zh">源码</span><span data-lang="en">Source</span></button>
        <button class="btn pl-btn" data-stage="ast">AST</button>
        <button class="btn pl-btn" data-stage="code">Code Object</button>
        <button class="btn pl-btn" data-stage="frame">Frame</button>
        <button class="btn pl-btn" data-stage="eval">ceval Loop</button>
      </div>
      <svg id="pl-svg" viewBox="0 0 800 300" class="w-full h-80 viz-stage"></svg>
    </div>

    <!-- 解释型语言的真相 -->
    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">"解释型"的真相：编译 + 解释两段式</span><span slot="en">The Truth About "Interpreted": Compile + Interpret</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">严格的"逐行解释"几乎不存在。现代语言按<b>编译时机</b>分三类：<b>AOT</b>（C/C++/Rust：运行前编译为机器码）、<b>JIT</b>（JVM/V8/PyPy：运行时编译热点为机器码）、<b>字节码解释</b>（CPython：运行前编译为字节码，运行时由 VM 解释）。CPython 属于第三类——它<b>有</b>编译器（<code>compile.c</code>），只是不编译到机器码，而是编译到一种<b>平台无关的中间指令</b>（字节码），再由 C 写的虚拟机解释执行。<code>.pyc</code> 文件就是缓存这套字节码，避免重复编译。</span><span slot="en">Strict "line-by-line interpretation" barely exists. Modern languages split by <b>compile timing</b>: <b>AOT</b> (C/C++/Rust: compile to machine code before run), <b>JIT</b> (JVM/V8/PyPy: compile hotspots to machine code at runtime), <b>bytecode interpretation</b> (CPython: compile to bytecode before run, interpret via VM at runtime). CPython is the third type — it <b>has</b> a compiler (<code>compile.c</code>), but compiles to <b>platform-independent intermediate instructions</b> (bytecode) instead of machine code, interpreted by a C-written VM. <code>.pyc</code> files cache this bytecode to avoid recompiling.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">模型</span><span slot="en">Model</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">代表</span><span slot="en">Example</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">编译产物</span><span slot="en">Output</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">运行机制</span><span slot="en">Runtime</span></Bilingual></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">AOT</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">C / C++ / Rust</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">机器码 (.exe)</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">CPU 直接执行</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-primary-cyan">字节码解释</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">CPython</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">字节码 (.pyc)</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">VM 大循环解释</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-primary-purple">JIT</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">PyPy / V8 / JVM</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">机器码 (运行时)</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">热点编译后执行</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber">混合</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">.NET / Dalvik</td><td class="py-2 pr-4 font-mono">字节码 + JIT</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">解释 + 热点编译</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 字节码与 Code Object -->
    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">字节码与 Code Object</span><span slot="en">Bytecode & Code Object</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">编译器把 AST 翻译成一系列<b>指令</b>（如 <code>LOAD_FAST</code>、<code>BINARY_ADD</code>、<code>RETURN_VALUE</code>），每条指令 1 字节操作码 + 可选参数。一个函数的全部字节码、常量表（<code>co_consts</code>）、变量名表（<code>co_names</code>/​<code>co_varnames</code>）打包成一个 <b>Code Object</b>。Code Object 是<b>不可变</b>的——这也是 <code>.pyc</code> 可缓存的原因：只要源码和解释器版本没变，字节码就不变。</span><span slot="en">The compiler translates the AST into a sequence of <b>instructions</b> (e.g. <code>LOAD_FAST</code>, <code>BINARY_ADD</code>, <code>RETURN_VALUE</code>), each 1-byte opcode + optional arg. A function's bytecode, constant table (<code>co_consts</code>), and name tables (<code>co_names</code>/<code>co_varnames</code>) are bundled into a <b>Code Object</b>. Code Objects are <b>immutable</b> — that's why <code>.pyc</code> caches work: bytecode is stable as long as source and interpreter version don't change.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <CodeTabs
  cpp={`<pre><code>// CPython 中 Code Object 的 C 定义（简化自 Include/cpython/code.h）
// 一个 PyCodeObject 封装了"一个函数/模块"的全部可执行信息

struct PyCodeObject &#123;
    PyObject_HEAD               // ob_refcnt + ob_type（见对象模型页）
    int        co_argcount;     // 位置参数个数
    int        co_nlocals;      // 局部变量槽位数
    int        co_stacksize;    // 值栈最大深度（编译期算出）
    int        co_flags;        // CO_VARARGS / CO_GENERATOR 等标志
    PyObject  *co_code;         // 字节码字节串（bytes，不可变）
    PyObject  *co_consts;       // 常量表（元组）：数字、字符串、嵌套 Code
    PyObject  *co_names;        // 全局/属性名表
    PyObject  *co_varnames;     // 局部变量名表
    PyObject  *co_freevars;     // 闭包捕获的变量名
    PyObject  *co_cellvars;     // 被内层闭包引用的变量名
    PyObject  *co_filename;     // 源文件名（用于 traceback）
    PyObject  *co_name;         // 函数名
    int        co_firstlineno;  // 源码起始行号
    // ... 其他用于 PEP 657 位置信息、异常表等
&#125;;

// 关键：co_stacksize 是编译期静态算出的
// VM 据此一次性分配好值栈数组，运行时无需动态扩容
// 这也是 Python 没有"栈溢出"而是有"递归深度限制"的原因</code></pre>`}
  py={`<pre><code># 用 dis 模块查看字节码——Python 程序员的"反汇编器"
import dis

def add(a, b):
    c = a + b
    return c

# 查看函数的 Code Object 属性
co = add.__code__
print(co.co_varnames)   # ('a', 'b', 'c')
print(co.co_consts)     # (None,)   —— None 是隐式 return
print(co.co_stacksize)  # 2         —— 值栈最多 2 深度
print(co.co_argcount)   # 2

# 反汇编：看 VM 实际要执行的指令序列
dis.dis(add)
#  2           0 LOAD_FAST                0 (a)
#              2 LOAD_FAST                1 (b)
#              4 BINARY_ADD               # 弹出 a,b，压入 a+b
#              6 STORE_FAST               2 (c)
#  3           8 LOAD_FAST                2 (c)
#             10 RETURN_VALUE             # 弹出栈顶作为返回值

# 左列 = 源码行号；中间 = 字节码偏移；右列 = 操作码 + 参数
# 这套指令就是 .pyc 里存的全部内容</code></pre>`}
      />
    </section>

    <!-- CPython 虚拟机实现 -->
    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">CPython 虚拟机：栈式大循环</span><span slot="en">CPython VM: Stack-Based Big Loop</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">CPython VM 是<b>栈式</b>（stack-based）而非寄存器式——指令不直接寻址寄存器，而是操作一个<b>值栈</b>：<code>LOAD_*</code> 压栈、<code>BINARY_*</code> 弹出操作数计算后压回结果。VM 的核心是 <code>Python/ceval.c</code> 里一个巨大的 <code>switch(opcode)</code> 循环：<b>取指 → 译码 → 执行 → 推进 PC</b>，周而复始。每条字节码指令都会<b>重新进入</b>这个 switch——这就是 CPython 比 JIT 慢的根源：每条指令都付出一次分支预测 + 一次函数调用般的开销，而 JIT 把热点编译成了连续的机器码。</span><span slot="en">CPython VM is <b>stack-based</b>, not register-based — instructions don't address registers but operate on a <b>value stack</b>: <code>LOAD_*</code> pushes, <code>BINARY_*</code> pops operands, computes, pushes back. The VM core is a giant <code>switch(opcode)</code> loop in <code>Python/ceval.c</code>: <b>fetch → decode → execute → advance PC</b>, ad infinitum. Each bytecode re-enters this switch — the root cause of CPython being slower than JIT: each instruction pays a branch prediction + call-like overhead, while JIT compiles hotspots into contiguous machine code.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <CodeTabs
  cpp={`<pre><code>// ceval.c 的核心循环（极度简化，省略内联缓存/预测/信号检查）
// 真实代码用 "computed goto"（GCC 扩展）替代 switch 以提升分支预测

PyObject* PyEval_EvalFrame(PyFrameObject *f) &#123;
    // 取出本帧的字节码与值栈
    PyObject **stack_pointer = f->f_valuestack;
    PyObject **fastlocals   = f->f_localsplus;
    _Py_CODEUNIT *code      = f->f_code->co_code;
    int next_instr = 0;

    for (;;) &#123;
        _Py_CODEUNIT word = code[next_instr++];  // 取指
        int opcode = _Py_OPCODE(word);            // 译码
        int oparg  = _Py_OPARG(word);

        switch (opcode) &#123;
        case LOAD_FAST: &#123;            // 压入局部变量
            PyObject *v = fastlocals[oparg];
            Py_INCREF(v);
            *stack_pointer++ = v;
            break;
        &#125;
        case STORE_FAST: &#123;            // 弹出并存入局部变量
            PyObject *v = *--stack_pointer;
            Py_XDECREF(fastlocals[oparg]);
            fastlocals[oparg] = v;        // 不增引用（fast 槽特殊处理）
            break;
        &#125;
        case BINARY_ADD: &#123;            // 弹两个，相加，压回
            PyObject *r = *--stack_pointer;
            PyObject *l = *--stack_pointer;
            PyObject *res = PyNumber_Add(l, r);  // 走类型系统 tp_add
            Py_DECREF(l); Py_DECREF(r);
            *stack_pointer++ = res;
            break;
        &#125;
        case RETURN_VALUE: &#123;
            PyObject *v = *--stack_pointer;
            return v;                     // 退出本帧
        &#125;
        // ... 共约 200 条指令 ...
        &#125;
    &#125;
&#125;

// 关键开销点：
// 1. 每条指令一次 switch 分支（computed goto 优化后仍有跳转）
// 2. 每个对象操作一次 Py_INCREF/Py_DECREF（引用计数开销）
// 3. BINARY_ADD 走 PyNumber_Add —— 动态类型分发，非直接 CPU add
// 这三点叠加，使 Python 比 C 慢 30-100 倍</code></pre>`}
  py={`<pre><code># 亲身体验栈式执行：值栈的状态变化
# 代码:  c = a + b * 2
#
# 字节码:
#   LOAD_FAST  a        栈: [a]
#   LOAD_FAST  b        栈: [a, b]
#   LOAD_CONST 2        栈: [a, b, 2]
#   BINARY_MULTIPLY     栈: [a, b*2]      弹 b,2 压 b*2
#   BINARY_ADD          栈: [a+b*2]       弹 a,b*2 压和
#   STORE_FAST c        栈: []            弹出存入 c

import dis
dis.dis(compile("c = a + b * 2", "&lt;str&gt;", "exec"))

# 对比：寄存器式 VM（如 Lua 5.0+、Dalvik）只需 2-3 条指令
#   R0 = getglobal a
#   R1 = getglobal b
#   R1 = R1 * 2
#   R0 = R0 + R1
#   setglobal c R0
# 寄存器式指令少但每条更长；栈式指令多但编码紧凑
# CPython 选栈式是因为实现简单、代码紧凑（历史决定）

# 体验"每条指令都有开销"：
python -X importtime your_script.py   # 看 import 耗时
python -m cProfile your_script.py     # 看函数级耗时</code></pre>`}
      />
    </section>

    <!-- 帧栈与函数调用 -->
    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">帧栈：函数调用的载体</span><span slot="en">Frame Stack: The Carrier of Calls</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">每次函数调用，VM 创建一个 <b>Frame</b>（<code>PyFrameObject</code>），压入<b>帧栈</b>。Frame 持有：本函数的 Code Object、值栈、局部变量槽、返回地址（字节码偏移）。函数返回时弹帧、恢复调用者的值栈与 PC。递归过深会<b>耗尽帧栈</b>——CPython 用 <code>sys.getrecursionlimit()</code>（默认 1000）保护 C 栈不溢出。<b>生成器</b>和<b>协程</b>的本质就是"可挂起的 Frame"：挂起时保留值栈与 PC，恢复时重新压回帧栈继续执行。</span><span slot="en">Each function call creates a <b>Frame</b> (<code>PyFrameObject</code>), pushed onto the <b>frame stack</b>. A frame holds: the function's Code Object, value stack, local slots, return address (bytecode offset). On return, the frame pops, restoring the caller's stack and PC. Deep recursion can <b>exhaust the frame stack</b> — CPython guards the C stack via <code>sys.getrecursionlimit()</code> (default 1000). <b>Generators</b> and <b>coroutines</b> are essentially "suspendable frames": on suspend, the value stack and PC are preserved; on resume, the frame is pushed back and execution continues.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <pre class="glass p-4 overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code><span class="text-func-green"># 生成器 = 可挂起的 Frame</span>
def counter():
    n = 0
    while True:
        yield n          <span class="text-ink-muted"># 挂起：保存 Frame（n、PC、值栈），返回值给调用者</span>
        n += 1           <span class="text-ink-muted"># 恢复：Frame 重新压栈，从 yield 之后继续</span>

gen = counter()
print(next(gen))  <span class="text-func-amber"># 0 —— 创建 Frame，执行到 yield，挂起</span>
print(next(gen))  <span class="text-func-amber"># 1 —— 恢复 Frame，n+=1，循环到下一个 yield</span>

<span class="text-primary-cyan"># async/await 是同一套机制的语义升级</span>
<span class="text-ink-muted"># await 本质：挂起当前 Frame，让出事件循环，等 Future 就绪后恢复</span>

<span class="text-func-red"># 递归限制：保护 C 栈</span>
import sys
print(sys.getrecursionlimit())  <span class="text-func-amber"># 1000</span>
def recurse(n): return recurse(n+1)
recurse(0)  <span class="text-func-red"># RecursionError: 帧栈超限（不是内存溢出，是保护）</span>

<span class="text-primary-purple"># sys.setrecursionlimit 可调高，但有 C 栈溢出崩溃风险</span></code></pre>
      <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">关联阅读：<a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/py-objects">对象模型与内存</a>讲解 <code>PyObject</code> 与引用计数；<a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/py-optimization">性能优化</a>讲解为何这套 VM 慢、如何优化。</span><span slot="en">Related: <a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/py-objects">Object Model & Memory</a> for <code>PyObject</code> & refcounting; <a class="text-primary-cyan underline" href="/topics/py-optimization">Performance</a> for why this VM is slow and how to optimize.</span></Bilingual></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
